11. **Meta Graph API license:** Depends on Meta''s product continuing; no backup scenario.
12. **Munich office lease:** 8-year term with limited tenant break clause, €340k p.a., exit only if revenue declines >30% over 2 years.
13. **2 key-person contracts** (CTO + Head of Product): Include change-of-control "golden parachutes" with combined severance ~€800k, plus accelerated vesting on outstanding options.

