16. Artemio acquired 3 companies in 4 years (two hire-acqs, one product-acq)—integration docs sparse; some employee contracts still under old structures.

**Deal context:**
- US buyer plans product integration with own HR suite portfolio in 12–18 months
- Buyer has loosely committed to honoring CoC clauses in prior EU acquisitions
- Timeline is aggressive—signing within 8 weeks

## Your Task

