# Launching a Premium Tier: Positioning, Pricing Story, and Sales Enablement

## Context

**Lattica** is a B2B project-management SaaS (€32M ARR, 2,400 customers, mostly SMB). Sales has spent 9 months losing 7-figure deals to enterprise competitors because Lattica had no premium tier. Engineering has now built **"Lattica Enterprise"** — SSO, advanced permissions, audit logs, dedicated CSM, 99.95% SLA. Pricing: from €19/seat (Pro) to **€48/seat (Enterprise)**.

