# Inbound Pipeline Down 40%: Rebuild the SDR Motion in 6 Weeks

## Context

**Threadly** is a B2B HR SaaS (€18M ARR, ~600 SMB and mid-market customers). Inbound MQLs were the engine: ~480/month converting to ~95 SQLs and ~22 closed-won. **In Q1, MQLs dropped to 290/month** and the SDR team''s connect rate also slipped. Pipeline is now ~€1.1M short of the H1 target.

The new VP Sales (you report to her) has given you 6 weeks to rebuild the SDR motion. You have 7 SDRs (3 senior, 4 ramping), an AE team of 9 (split SMB and mid-market), and a marketing team that''s also under pressure.

