| MQL-to-call-booked rate | 18% | 11% |
| Outbound call-booked rate | 5.2% | 3.1% |
| AE-accepted SQLs | 19/wk | 9/wk |
| Speed-to-lead (median) | 7 min | 23 min |
| SDR daily activities (median) | 78 | 52 |

**What you know:**

- The marketing team paused 2 high-volume paid channels (cost-per-MQL exploded)
- 2 senior SDRs left in the last quarter; 4 hires ramping unevenly (1 strong, 2 OK, 1 struggling)
- The new outbound sequence the previous lead deployed has open rates of 19% (industry: 32%) — copy looks generic
