- AE reject rate is a signal of quality breakdown — but tightening too far could mean SDRs miss their meeting quotas. Where''s the line?
- Speed-to-lead jumped from 7 min to 23 min. Is that a routing problem, a capacity problem, or a discipline problem? Different fixes.
- 6 weeks is short. What do you NOT do (e.g., a full sequence A/B test takes 6 weeks alone)?

