**Cynara Pharma** (mid-sized European specialty pharma, oncology + auto-immune focus) has just received EMA approval for a **second indication** of their existing immunology drug **Verifex**: now also approved for moderate-to-severe ulcerative colitis (originally approved for psoriatic arthritis). Launch in Germany (lead market) is in **12 weeks**.

